    <div class="main review-item" id="2215719">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2215719/" class="title-link">这是一本皇汉民族主义奴才们不原意读的佳作</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2215719"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2164580-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">tradition</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-08-11"
      class="main-meta">2009-08-11 14:28:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2215719_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  皇汉民族主义奴才请愿去看老奴才钱穆写的把中国本族的封建皇帝写成无私心的共产主义社会的垃圾货色，也没有这个勇气来阅读一下客观评论中西差异的书籍    　　　　  　　　　钱穆在论及清朝的密奏制度时手舞足蹈，写到“其他旁人都不知道，秘密政治当然是一种法术，而不能是一...

